<br>
The solution?  Group with SH's or Divine Souls.  Bring in some outsiders and before anyone even stands up to pull, lay down the law.  The folks are doing this, these folks are doing this, your doing this.  Assist XXX, don't attack anything till they do.<br>
<br>
Then, If you can't change your people, change you people.  Remove them from the group, or yourself.<br>
<br>
I've done it in the past.  I simply say, &quot;I'm looking for a TEAM, not a GROUP.  Thanks all and good luck.&quot; and move on. <p><center><img src="http://members.home.net/craigfry23/stained.gif" 
